1) to list out all the files present in current 
directory

ls *

ls file1

2) list out all the files with some extension

ls *.*

3) list out all .txt files
ls *.txt

4) list out only .java files

ls *.java

5) list out files starting with letter a 

ls a*

6) list out all the files starts with t and ends with s

ls t*s
7) list out all the files whose name contains only two characters

ls ??
8) list out all the files whose name contains only three characters

ls ?? ?

9) list out all the file where filenames contains 2 char and first character should be x

ls x?

10) list out all the file where filename contains atleast 3 chars

ls ???*
